title: Otorabad
text: Otorabad (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Otorābād and Otrābād) is a village in <a href="Quchan%20Atiq%20Rural%20District">Quchan Atiq Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Quchan%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Quchan%20County">Quchan County</a>, <a href="Razavi%20Khorasan%20Province">Razavi Khorasan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 623, in 179 families.
